latestPosts.caption:
Boulevard of fulfilled dreams 🥹💚
.
Once upon a time a kid with smudged kajal and ‘Basket Case’ playing on her discman never imagined she’d grow up to stand front row at a Green Day concert. 🥹
@greenday wasn’t just a band; they raised me. 🫶 From putting it in my 12th Standard farewell speech to screaming ‘it’s something unpredictable, but in the end, it’s right’ with thousands of strangers, I knew this was exactly where I was meant to be. 🥰🥹💚
One day, when my future kids roll their eyes at us, I’ll remind them that their parents were the cool millennials who camped out, stood front row, and lost their voices singing 21 Guns and literally had the “Time of Their lives”. 😬🥹😎
.
@lollaindia #lollapalooza #lollaindia
